Description: Facial capture CLI and PAM module powered by V4L2 + dlib
 Provides the `chissu-cli` capture/enrollment helper plus the `pam_chissu`
 authentication module. Packages manage `/etc/chissu-pam/config.toml`, stage
 embeddings under `/var/lib/chissu-pam/`, and download the required dlib
 landmark + encoder model weights during installation.
